text: int main ( ) { int t ; scanf ( "%d" , & t ) ; while ( t -- ) { int a , b , n , gcd , lcm ; scanf ( "%d%d" , & a , & b ) ; n = a > b ? a : b ; for ( int i = 1 ; i <= n ; i ++ ) { if ( a % i == 0 && b % i == 0 ) { gcd = i ; } } lcm = ( a * b ) / gcd ; printf ( "%d %d\n" , gcd , lcm ) ; } return 0 ; }
